<item>
            <title>[LU-1763] enable Job Stats by default in test framework</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1763</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As shown in bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1735&quot; title=&quot;sanityn 18 hung&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1735&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1735&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we are not running Job Stats under a variety of test workloads.  It would make sense to enable Job Stats by default in the test framework using the &quot;procname_uid&quot; type, so that it is always active and being tested by all of the different code paths.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
